---
import TemplateLayout from "@/templates/accounting-zen/TemplateLayout.astro";
---

<TemplateLayout
  title="Services | Zen Ledger Advisory"
  description="Tax, Audit, and Advisory — the core disciplines of Zen Ledger Advisory."
  active="services"
  canonicalPath="/templates/accounting-zen/services"
>
<main class="pt-40">
<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="content-frame px-margin-mobile md:px-0 mb-section-gap fade-in">
<div class="max-w-3xl">
<p class="text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-on-surface-variant mb-6">Expertise Overview</p>
<h1 class="font-zl-display text-zl-display mb-12">Structured Clarity.</h1>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
                    In the landscape of modern finance, complexity is often mistaken for depth. We navigate through the noise to provide a framework of surgical precision, ensuring your capital remains a silent engine of growth.
                </p>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Services Grid: Pure Typographic Hierarchy -->
<section class="content-frame px-margin-mobile md:px-0 border-t border-outline-variant pt-24 mb-section-gap">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-0">
<!-- Tax Strategy -->
<div class="md:pr-12 md:pb-0 pb-16 border-b md:border-b-0 border-outline-variant md:relative">
<div class="hidden md:block absolute right-0 top-0 bottom-0 vertical-line"></div>
<span class="text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm text-on-surface-variant opacity-50 block mb-12">01 /</span>
<h3 class="font-zl-display text-zl-headline-lg mb-8">Tax Strategy</h3>
<p class="text-zl-body-md font-zl-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                        Multijurisdictional optimization for the modern enterprise. We mitigate exposure through structural foresight rather than reactive accounting.
                    </p>
<ul class="space-y-4">
<li class="text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm flex items-center gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[16px]">arrow_forward</span>
                            GLOBAL COMPLIANCE
                        </li>
<li class="text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm flex items-center gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[16px]">arrow_forward</span>
                            ESTATE OPTIMIZATION
                        </li>
<li class="text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm flex items-center gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[16px]">arrow_forward</span>
                            R&amp;D TAX CREDITS
                        </li>
</ul>
</div>
<!-- Audit & Assurance -->
<div class="md:px-12 md:pb-0 py-16 border-b md:border-b-0 border-outline-variant md:relative">
<div class="hidden md:block absolute right-0 top-0 bottom-0 vertical-line"></div>
<span class="text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm text-on-surface-variant opacity-50 block mb-12">02 /</span>
<h3 class="font-zl-display text-zl-headline-lg mb-8">Audit &amp; Assurance</h3>
<p class="text-zl-body-md font-zl-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                        Transparency as a tool for trust. Our audits provide more than compliance; they offer a definitive map of your operational integrity.
                    </p>
<ul class="space-y-4">
<li class="text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm flex items-center gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[16px]">arrow_forward</span>
                            STATUTORY AUDITS
                        </li>
<li class="text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm flex items-center gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[16px]">arrow_forward</span>
                            RISK ASSESSMENT
                        </li>
<li class="text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm flex items-center gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[16px]">arrow_forward</span>
                            ESG REPORTING
                        </li>
</ul>
</div>
<!-- Wealth Preservation -->
<div class="md:px-12 md:pb-0 py-16 border-b md:border-b-0 border-outline-variant md:relative">
<div class="hidden md:block absolute right-0 top-0 bottom-0 vertical-line"></div>
<span class="text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm text-on-surface-variant opacity-50 block mb-12">03 /</span>
<h3 class="font-zl-display text-zl-headline-lg mb-8">Wealth Preservation</h3>
<p class="text-zl-body-md font-zl-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                        The art of keeping what you build. We design bespoke legacy structures that withstand economic volatility and generational shifts.
                    </p>
<ul class="space-y-4">
<li class="text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm flex items-center gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[16px]">arrow_forward</span>
                            FAMILY OFFICE SERVICES
                        </li>
<li class="text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm flex items-center gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[16px]">arrow_forward</span>
                            TRUST PLANNING
                        </li>
<li class="text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm flex items-center gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[16px]">arrow_forward</span>
                            ASSET PROTECTION
                        </li>
</ul>
</div>
<!-- Corporate Advisory -->
<div class="md:pl-12 md:pb-0 pt-16 md:pt-0">
<span class="text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm text-on-surface-variant opacity-50 block mb-12">04 /</span>
<h3 class="font-zl-display text-zl-headline-lg mb-8">Corporate Advisory</h3>
<p class="text-zl-body-md font-zl-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                        Strategic guidance at the intersection of capital and growth. We advise on M&amp;A, restructuring, and value enhancement initiatives.
                    </p>
<ul class="space-y-4">
<li class="text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm flex items-center gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[16px]">arrow_forward</span>
                            M&amp;A TRANSACTIONS
                        </li>
<li class="text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm flex items-center gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[16px]">arrow_forward</span>
                            DEBT RESTRUCTURING
                        </li>
<li class="text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm flex items-center gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[16px]">arrow_forward</span>
                            STRATEGIC VALUATION
                        </li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Visual Anchor Section -->
<section class="content-frame px-margin-mobile md:px-0 mb-section-gap">
<div class="relative h-[600px] w-full bg-surface-container overflow-hidden group">
<div class="absolute inset-0 grayscale transition-transform duration-1000 group-hover:scale-105" data-alt="A minimalist architectural interior with vast concrete walls and a single shard of natural light illuminating a dark void. The scene is captured in high contrast monochrome, emphasizing the clean lines and geometric shadows. The aesthetic is serene, professional, and sophisticated, reflecting the concept of Shibui and the precision of high-end financial advisory." style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDhgPrZms-TFD2_0SIFOz_fYTnSQO6mLZ3v9a2-WMRTh7jrnm6AmmtLIlwONJKGM8ujY8NOpLeGkx4LV8ntwxVSB7gekx5uF2f2_fyV8DSuV20YoBgQQbZuKGFLLnJYZBHuQDeoA0HEXk5begSR4cDzi9vMFnZDUKtTbd20p_JEU4HUv_M79-EQfez2r7pj9qvyVWXrjRfX1SqtjQWUbgXFCUg5BGNksMT-Fl-qW6eUHa7Mg4eYcVO6eZIKoV6NStpLN1rWdPTuwSU9')">
</div>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/10"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-12 left-12 max-w-lg">
<h2 class="text-background font-zl-display text-zl-headline-lg mb-4">Precision in Silence.</h2>
<p class="text-background/80 text-zl-body-md leading-relaxed">
                        Our approach is understated. We do not seek the spotlight; we build the foundations that allow your success to speak for itself.
                    </p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Call to Action -->
<section class="content-frame px-margin-mobile md:px-0 py-section-gap border-t border-outline-variant text-center">
<div class="max-w-xl mx-auto">
<h2 class="font-zl-display text-zl-headline-lg mb-8">Begin the Dialogue.</h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-12">Consultation is by appointment. We prioritize depth of partnership over breadth of client base.</p>
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center gap-6">
<a class="border border-primary px-12 py-4 text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-primary hover:text-on-primary transition-all duration-300" href="/templates/accounting-zen/contact">Request Appointment</a>
<a class="px-12 py-4 text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm uppercase tracking-widest hover:underline underline-offset-8 transition-all duration-300" href="/templates/accounting-zen/about">View Client Ethos</a>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</main>

</TemplateLayout>
